<div class="full-width-stripe value-prop-box">
	<div class="content">
		<h1>Peer-to-peer recruiting at its best</h1>
		<h2>Connect the development team directly to their respected peers</h2>
		
		<div class="value-prop-box-bullets">
			<div class="bullet-box beautiful-ads">
				<h3>Beautiful ads</h3>
				<span>Attract qualified developers with the best job postings in the world.</span>
			</div>
			<div class="bullet-box show-developers">
				<h3>Show developers why they want to work for you</h3>
				<span>Leverage your recruiting processes for better employer branding.</span>
			</div>
			<div class="bullet-box get-pinged">
				<h3>Get pinged by pros</h3>
				</span>Get the best candidates into a conversation with you.</span>
			</div>						
